{"tid":445270,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖咪拍拖囉，做乜撚野變左自動同居呀","createTime":"2017-10-23T08:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T17:13:29.000Z","uid":128894,"like":566,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"21ebb75faf7cd5e9a08a0cca97359deaeefab892","tid":445270,"uid":128894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解啲人一拍拖就覺得人地所有時間都要比哂你<br />\n放工要第一時間去搵你<br />\n同朋友出去食飯出街飲野你又要起度<br />\n<br />\n夜晚要訓<br />\n想返自己屋企靜下都比你閪面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實明明我都有屋企返，有屋企人要陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解要閪鳩我面呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去你屋企次次沖涼都要入埋黎一齊沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪痴撚線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日見都仲話無時間陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我搬左去你度架？<br />\n點解我唔知既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解我唔返得自己屋企？<br />\n去你度變撚左係我責任咁既？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係唔係個個拍拖都會自動將同居呢回事成立左？<br />\n係人都需要私人時間<br />\n未ready同你住你就收皮啦<br />\n閪乜撚野面姐？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班仆街究竟有冇理過另一半感受？<br />\n跟到咁緊咁貼做乜撚野呀？<br />\n醒下啦，你係獨立一個個體黎架屌你老母"},{"pid":"84be1e3c30353a7bb2ccc1c78da89569b1ed6483","tid":445270,"uid":76942,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"做咩咁話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15aa0b31f48eff495908a2264dd0c705cda3e3b9","tid":445270,"uid":48776,"like":20,"dislike":8,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:10:57.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好憤怒<br />\n想知樓豬係男定女"},{"pid":"01d6d63d1eb339e2994c8d896215b6d5a62389ae","tid":445270,"uid":148673,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n好多女一拍拖就無晒自己<br />\n好沉重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal