kgmoji\" /> 但我又覺得幾sweet既<br />\n可能因為都仲係半年咁上下熱戀期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我先一個月多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間唔中sweet囉<br />\n太過份會反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個月多啲咁好正常姐，熱戀期<br />\n半年後都仲係咁先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94940dc1947dcd71f1b75b7dd12d6fb0ccb592d3","tid":445270,"uid":28195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"我之前條女，成日西面，又煩，又中意發脾氣<br />\n<br />\n我on9，拍左好多年先識分手，之後兩條女都好正，脾氣好，搵到錢自給自足，仲要淫淫地。<br />\n<br />\n好後悔當時太遲分手"},{"pid":"a38b9cdb2fb0731273fb0935fcc6668904f1892f","tid":445270,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"咁咪分手囉  <br />\n<br />\n同一個人相處 冇話剩係可以要佢既好 唔要佢既壞<br />\n對每個人都係放上天秤稱過 先決定一唔一齊架啦<br />\n<br />\n你覺得佢衰既大於好既 咁咪分手搵過第二個囉<br />\n香港地女人都唔憂搵唔到仔 嘈乜野姐"},{"pid":"bf2623c98c5363733a1e50f6b9bf5377bdfd2b4e","tid":445270,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"如果想衝下事業的話，同呢d女一齊，唔整死你，都一身潺"},{"pid":"bdd3a01dd550c3171a1a72a353cac1a2379179fb","tid":445270,"uid":76942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做咩咁話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放我返屋企啦你</blockquote><br />\n但我好掛住你好想痴住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街死開呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj